H0.text: Mswati III is the king of which African country. Lesotho

H1.text: Mswati III is the king of which African country. Botswana

H2.text: Mswati III is the king of which African country. Zambia

H3.text: Mswati III is the king of which African country. Swasiland

A4.text: Mswati III is the Ngwenyama (King) of Eswatini and head of the Swazi royal family.

A5.text: Mswati III promulgated a decree renaming the country to Eswatini, from its previous name of Swaziland.
